{"tid":789653,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"對住咁嘅老母可以點","createTime":"2018-08-22T11:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T09:45:52.000Z","uid":185932,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c433f23ffa62c84eda26180a8ae44daf6fbc0eed","tid":789653,"uid":185932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"畢業到宜家都喺同一間公司做，<br />\n因為太過穩定同無挑戰所以決定跳出去startup闖一闖。<br />\n有offer之後衰口快快同咗老母講轉工嘅事，<br />\n然後佢就連續兩個禮拜講埋啲風涼說話。<br />\n又話我會失業俾人炒，<br />\n又話我on9辭職，<br />\n又話我自大以為自己好叻。<br />\n<br />\n其實本身自己都係好大勇氣跳出comfort zone，佢咁講完情緒好受影響。<br />\n想問下大家可以點調整心情？"},{"pid":"2f1e2306e609f379d2379b81fd020b6243c55c51","tid":789653,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"startup？ 有offer？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9760d7aef3515170e70c9d2031da4779129be8","tid":789653,"uid":22731,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"唔比家用 好心情～"},{"pid":"38517bd3ceb36ec1df2335d10dc12bf557745c5f","tid":789653,"uid":198783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"就咁睇都覺得佢控制欲極強<br />\n唔撚理佢就啱<br />\n必要時咪開佢波囉"},{"pid":"dd7731d0fd03098389bf302ba198423cd075c2a2","tid":789653,"uid":39261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"趁後生緊係闖一闖<br />\n唔通等老左先黎轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93e540bb75853b582b445494f8390ff97901eb4","tid":789653,"uid":185932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38517bd3ceb36ec1df2335d10dc12bf557745c5f","tid":789653,"uid":198783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"就咁睇都覺得佢控制欲極強<br />\n唔撚理佢就啱<br />\n必要時咪開佢波囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:45:01.000Z","msg":"其實點解啲老一輩係都要後生做啲穩穩陣陣嘅工呢？"},{"pid":"b53ca88c928aa09cabc64774de2824b3ccca253b","tid":789653,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor